ice%20changes%20I%20never%20used%20to%20notice%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20wife%20and%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-moved-small-town-lower-cost-living-benefits-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emoved%20from%20Calgary%20to%20Nelson%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20British%20Columbia%2C%20in%202017.%20The%20decision%20was%20a%20big%20one%2C%20and%20while%20it%20gave%20our%20family%20a%20lifestyle%20we%20love%2C%20it%20also%20put%20seven%20hours%20of%20highway%20between%20us%20and%20our%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20we%20don't%20see%20them%20every%20week%20or%20even%20every%20month%2C%20our%20time%20together%20has%20become%20more%20precious.%20When%20I%20was%20younger%2C%20aging%20seemed%20gradual%2C%20something%20everyone%20experienced%2C%20but%20far%20off%20in%20the%20distance.%20But%20now%2C%20since%20we%20only%20see%20my%20parents%20a%20few%20times%20a%20year%2C%20the%20changes%20they%20are%20going%20through%20have%20become%20more%20noticeable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20still%20healthy%20and%20active%2C%20but%20I%20find%20myself%20paying%20attention%20to%20their%20aging%20in%20a%20way%20I%20never%20did%20before.%20They%20have%20a%20little%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-stopped-dyeing-my-gray-hair-2-years-ago-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egray%20hair%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20walk%20a%20little%20slower%20up%20the%20stairs.%20Each%20visit%20reminds%20me%20that%20time%20is%20moving%20forward%2C%20whether%20I'm%20ready%20for%20it%20or%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227e0aa257-3975-40c3-8fdc-3ae7d52cbaf8%5C%22%3EWatching%20my%20kids%20grow%20makes%20time%20feel%20more%20tangible%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EParenting%20constantly%20reminds%20you%20how%20quickly%20life%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20see%20it%20in%20my%20own%20house%20every%20day.%20My%20daughter%20is%20becoming%20a%20young%20woman%20(she%20already%20rolls%20her%20eyes%20at%20every%20lame%20dad%20joke%20I%20make).%20My%20son%20spends%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcost-teens-social-lives-parent-money-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etime%20with%20his%20friends%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20he%20does%20following%20me%20around%20the%20house%20like%20he%20used%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20honest%2C%20it%20makes%20me%20sad.%20The%20stages%20I%20once%20thought%20would%20last%20forever%20are%20coming%20to%20a%20close%20almost%20overnight.%20But%20watching%20that%20happen%20with%20my%20kids%20has%20changed%20how%20I%20see%20my%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20years%2C%20my%20parents%20seemed%20fixed%20in%20my%20mind.%20They%20were%20simply%20Mom%20and%20Dad.%20The%20people%20who%20picked%20me%20up%20from%20soccer%20practice%2C%20taught%20me%20how%20to%20drive%2C%20and%20helped%20us%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmistakes-buying-first-starter-home-wrong-choice-los-angeles-regrets-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuy%20our%20first%20house%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20I%20realize%20they%20aren't%20frozen%20in%20those%20roles.%20They're%20getting%20older%2C%20and%20their%20lives%20are%20changing%20too.%20Somehow%2C%20it%20took%20becoming%20a%20parent%20myself%20to%20fully%20understand%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2269cb5bc8-cd06-4770-ad8e-561454a4f69d%5C%22%3EParenting%20has%20made%20me%20more%20grateful%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20my%20wife%20and%20I%20navigate%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchildcare-costs-without-grandparents-help-millennial-parents-boomers-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echallenges%20of%20raising%20kids%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20have%20a%20greater%20appreciation%20for%20what%20my%20parents%20did%20for%20my%20brothers%20and%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20also%20developed%20a%20better%20understanding%20of%20the%20sacrifices%20they%20made.%20All%20the%20worry%20and%20stress%20I%20caused%20them.%20The%20patience%20and%20selflessness%20they%20displayed%20over%20the%20years.%20The%20way%20they%20were%20always%20there%20for%20me%2C%20time%20after%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20as%20I%20watch%20my%20children%20slowly%20need%20me%20less%2C%20I%20realize%20my%20parents%20have%20been%20experiencing%20their%20own%20version%20of%20that%20process%20for%20years.%20The%20older%20my%20kids%20get%2C%20the%20more%20aware%20I%20become%20that%20life%20isn't%20moving%20in%20a%20single%20direction.%20It's%20happening%20on%20both%20ends%20at%20once.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20children%20are%20becoming%20more%20independent.%20My%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Folder-parents-pressure-having-kids-career-focused-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eparents%20are%20getting%20older%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20I'm%20standing%20somewhere%20in%20the%20middle%2C%20trying%20not%20to%20take%20either%20for%20granted.%20It's%20a%20strange%20place%20to%20be.%20But%20it's%20made%20me%20more%20present%20and%20appreciative%20for%20this%20one%2C%20beautiful%20chance%20at%20life%20we%20get.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkids-older-think-about-parents-aging-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783334461000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a46b043e3bd3a50082bfc0c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkids-older-think-about-parents-aging-2026-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20my%20kids%20are%20getting%20older%2C%20time%20is%20going%20more%20quickly.%20I'm%20realizing%20my%20parents'%20lives%20are%20changing%20and%20they're%20aging%2C%20too.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Adam%20Meyer)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Don't%20politicise%20matter'%3A%20Ram%20Mandir%20trust%20chief%20amid%20donation%20'theft'%20row%22%