stablish%20AI%20data%20centres%20in%20space%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783331603000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2026-07%2F06%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F1200X628%2F1783331048-3256.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ftechnology%2Fartificial-intelligence%2Fbeyond-earth-why-tech-companies-want-to-establish-ai-data-centres-in-space-126070600603_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20AI%20pushes%20power%20grids%20and%20land%20requirements%20to%20their%20limits%2C%20companies%20are%20exploring%20orbital%20data%20centres.%20Here's%20why%20space%20is%20becoming%20part%20of%20the%20AI%20infrastructure%20conversation%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ftechnology%2Fartificial-intelligence%2Fbeyond-earth-why-tech-companies-want-to-establish-ai-data-centres-in-space-126070600603_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Ftechnology%2Fartificial-intelligence%2Fbeyond-earth-why-tech-companies-want-to-establish-ai-data-centres-in-space-126070600603_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Ftechnology%2Fartificial-intelligence%2Fbeyond-earth-why-tech-companies-want-to-establish-ai-data-centres-in-space-126070600603_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delegation%2C%20trust%2C%20and%20a%20shared%20nickname%3A%20How%20two%20bankers%20co-lead%20a%20550-person%20JPMorgan%20team%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22John%20China%20and%20Andrew%20Kresse%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a457f86ec11c5f7e7fa7619%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJohn%20China%20and%20Andrew%20Kresse%20co-lead%20a%20team%20of%20more%20than%20550%20JPMorgan%20employees.%3Cp%3EJPMorgan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EJohn%20China%20and%20Andrew%20Kresse%20co-lead%20a%20global%20team%20of%20more%20than%20550%20people%20at%20JPMorgan.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Innovation%20Economy%20team%20banks%20high-growth%20startups%20and%20has%20grown%20rapidly%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EKresse%20and%20China%20told%20Business%20Insider%20how%20they%20use%20their%20distinct%20backgrounds%20to%20execute%20the%20strategy.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%20JPMorgan%20executives%20receive%20emails%20from%20a%20colleague%20who%20signs%20off%20in%20all%20caps%3A%20JACK.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJACK%2C%20however%2C%20isn't%20one%20person.%20It's%20the%20shared%20identity%20of%20John%20China%20and%20Andrew%20Kresse%2C%20who%20co-lead%20the%20bank's%20Innovation%20Economy%20team%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F10-best-banks-for-startups-according-to-founders-and-vcs-2025-8%3Futm_%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efounders%20and%20venture%20capital%20firms%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20nickname%20started%20as%20a%20practical%20solution%2C%20Kresse%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20kept%20on%20writing%20emails%20like%2C%20'Dear%20John%20and%20Andrew%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20was%20like%2C%20let's%20not%20waste%20time.%20Let's%20give%20them%20something%20easy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20acronym%20of%20their%20initials%20%E2%80%94%20John%2C%20Andrew%2C%20China%2C%20Kresse%20%E2%80%94%20also%20reflects%20the%20united%20leadership%20from%20the%20two%20very%20different%20bankers.%20A%20Silicon%20Valley%20veteran%20recruited%20from%20SVB%20and%20a%20nearly%20two-decade%20JPMorgan%20executive%2C%20they%20have%20spent%20the%20past%20year%20figuring%20out%20how%20to%20co-lead%20a%20fast-growing%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20Silicon%20Valley%20Bank%20collapsed%20and%20JPMorgan%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffirst-republic-bank-taken-jpmorgan-fdic-fails-find-buyer-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebought%20First%20Republic%20Bank%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20firm%20has%20aggressively%20grown%20its%20Innovation%20Economy%20team.%20They're%20competing%20with%20the%20likes%20of%20Goldman%20Sachs%2C%20Morgan%20Stanley%2C%20and%20Citi%20to%20bank%20startups%20from%20the%20earliest%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina%20became%20a%20leader%20on%20the%20team%20in%202023%20after%2027%20years%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F5-lessons-every-founder-should-have-learned-from-silicon-valley-bank-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESilicon%20Valley%20Bank%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Kresse%20became%20a%20co-head%20in%202025.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETogether%2C%20they%20oversee%20more%20than%20550%20people%20advising%20more%20than%2011%2C000%20companies%20and%20are%20squarely%20focused%20on%20executing%20the%20long-term%20strategy%20and%20scaling%20the%20team.%20Part%20of%20that%20means%20undercutting%20the%20narrative%20that%20JPMorgan%20is%20best%20for%20established%20companies%20looking%20to%20go%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20founders%20to%20understand%20that%20we're%20here%20for%20them%20from%20the%20beginning%2C%20and%20that's%20probably%20something%20that%20the%20industry%20doesn't%20yet%20fully%20understand%2C%26quot%3B%20China%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229661e018-2347-47b4-800e-c9d4ed580c21%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EGrowing%20JPMorgan's%20startup%20business%20together%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20it%20started%20in%202016%2C%20the%20Innovation%20Economy%20business%20rapidly%20expanded%20from%202023%20to%20last%20year%2C%20quadrupling%20its%20client%20base%20and%20hiring%20more%20than%20200%20bankers%20and%20leaders.%20The%20team%20banks%20companies%20pre-seed%20through%20%242%20billion%20in%20revenue%20or%20an%20IPO%2C%20when%20they%20transition%20over%20to%20JPMorgan's%20corporate%20banking%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20have%20built%20the%20business%20on%20opposite%20sides%20of%20the%20country.%20China%20is%20on%20the%20West%20Coast%20and%20brings%20decades%20of%20experience%20building%20relationships%20in%20the%20venture%20community.%20Kresse%20is%20on%20the%20East%20Coast%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjpmorgan-women-ceo-succession-race-dimon-rohrbaugh-petno-lake-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eknows%20JPMorgan%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20his%20years%20expanding%20commercial%20banking%20internationally%20and%20his%20time%20as%20the%20CEO%20of%20Chase%20Business%20Banking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20divide%20and%20conquer%2C%20and%20you%20have%20to%20delegate%2C%26quot%3B%20Kresse%20said%2C%20especially%20on%20such%20a%20large%20and%20global%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20leaders%20don't%20have%20a%20highly%20structured%20way%20of%20communicating%2C%20but%20they're%20always%20available%20by%20phone%20or%20email%20on%20days%20when%20they're%20not%20physically%20together%2C%20Kresse%20said.%20Their%20conversations%20range%20from%20guiding%20the%20team%20and%20making%20hiring%20decisions%2C%20to%20brainstorming%20client%20solutions%20and%20tackling%20internal%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20like%20a%20pair%20of%20coaches%20calling%20audibles%20as%20the%20game%20unfolds%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20often%20travel%20separately%2C%20and%20who%20goes%20where%20is%20dictated%20by%20their%20distinct%20strengths%2C%20but%20they%20always%20reference%20JACK%2C%20China%20added.%20When%20they're%20not%20on%20the%20road%2C%20living%20on%20opposite%20coasts%20extends%20their%20joint%20workday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20China%20sees%20it%2C%20the%20key%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspotify-comcast-oracle-announce-co-ceo-model-leadership-bet-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emaking%20joint%20leadership%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20especially%20in%20such%20a%20fast-paced%20business%2C%20is%20to%20%26quot%3Balways%20presume%20innocence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaybe%20someone%20gets%20left%20off%20an%20email%20or%20a%20team%20isn't%20looped%20in%20quickly%20enough%2C%20and%20we%20assume%20positive%20intent%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20email%2C%20he%20added%20that%20people%20%26quot%3Boften%20think%20co-leadership%20means%20competition%20or%20confusion%2C%20but%20it's%20really%20about%20collaboration.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHaving%20two%20of%20us%20with%20different%20perspectives%20helps%20us%20solve%20problems%2C%20motivate%20our%20team%2Cm%20and%20spend%20more%20time%20with%20them%20and%20with%20clients%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20officially%20becoming%20co-leaders%2C%20the%20duo%20got%20to%20know%20each%20other%20partly%20through%20building%20out%20client%20advisory%20boards%20abroad%2C%20in%20Europe%20and%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20knew%20John%20was%20a%20good%20guy%20before%20we%20were%20co-heads%2C%20which%20is%20always%20the%20best%20thing%3A%20to%20have%20an%20informal%20relationship%20and%20partnership%20before%20anything%20formal%2C%26quot%3B%20Kresse%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20relationship%20extends%20beyond%20work.%20When%20they're%20not%20talking%20business%2C%20Kresse%20said%2C%20they're%20swapping%20stories%20about%20their%20kids%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3BJohn's%20are%20a%20bit%20older%2C%20so%20I%20get%20to%20hear%20some%20of%20his%20lessons%20learned%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20and%20trading%20friendly%20jabs%20over%20football.%20China%20roots%20for%20the%20Raiders%3B%20Kresse%20is%20a%20lifelong%20Bills%20fan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bf22ec63-ad89-498f-a81c-1265223061f1%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20%26quot%3Bathletic%20stance%26quot%3B%20for%20AI%20startups%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20area%20of%20their%20business%20is%20moving%20faster%20than%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20Innovation%20Economy%20team%20banks%20companies%20across%20eight%20sectors%20%E2%80%94%20applied%20tech%2C%20health%20tech%2C%20and%20life%20sciences%2C%20to%20name%20a%20few%20%E2%80%94%20China%20and%20Kresse%20said%20they've%20never%20seen%20anything%20like%20the%20pace%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwall-street-banks-ai-strategy-jpmorgan-goldman-citi-bofa-2026%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20AI%20boom%3C%2Fa%3E.%20There%20can%20be%20as%20many%20as%2010%20new%20AI%20companies%20in%20a%20week%2C%20Kresse%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20team%20isn't%20responsible%20for%20picking%20winners%20and%20losers%20%E2%80%94%20they'll%20work%20with%20companies%20opening%20their%20first%20checking%20account%20and%20companies%20getting%20ready%20to%20go%20public.%20China%20said%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-startup-moving-into-smaller-neighborhoods-changing-office-culture-sf-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enext%20generation%20of%20AI%20companies%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20keep%20an%20eye%20on%20are%20those%20building%20agents%20that%20will%20sit%20atop%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20those%20founders%20who%2C%20if%20all%20goes%20well%2C%20will%20develop%20relationships%20with%20China%20and%20Kresse's%20team%2C%20and%2C%20by%20extension%2C%20JPMorgan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20take%20an%20athletic%20stance%2C%26quot%3B%20China%20said%20about%20AI%20companies%3Cstrong%3E.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20His%20team%20is%20staying%20ready%20to%20support%20companies%20hoping%20to%20become%20the%20next%20OpenAI%20through%20their%20%26quot%3Baccelerated%20growth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjpmorgan-startup-venture-banking-john-china-andrew-kresse-leadership-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783331521000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a457f86ec11c5f7e7fa7619%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F