rd.com%2Famp%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Fprestige-estates-acquires-50-stake-in-advent-hotels-for-504-crore-126070600494_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Companies%20are%20buying%20AI%20tools.%20That%20doesn't%20mean%20they%20know%20what%20to%20do%20with%20them.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227697%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22AI%20tools%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4ab86be3bd3a50082c0637%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225773%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EOscar%20Wong%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ENew%20reports%20from%20BCG%2C%20Ramp%2C%20and%20Revelio%20Labs%20look%20at%20AI%20deployment%20at%20companies.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20reports%20found%20that%20AI%20returns%20don't%20come%20from%20deployment%20%E2%80%94%20they%20come%20from%20strategy.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20right%20way%20to%20deploy%20AI%20is%20through%20enacting%20organizational%20change%2C%20they%20found.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20have%20spent%20the%20past%20two%20years%20racing%20to%20deploy%20chatbots%2C%20coding%20assistants%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-coding-agents-cursor-human-review-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20agents%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20their%20workers.%20Two%20new%20reports%2C%20however%2C%20suggest%20that%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Edeploying%20AI%20tools%20is%20the%20easy%20part.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hard%20part%20is%20using%20them%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERamp%2C%20a%20financial%20technology%20company%2C%20and%20Revelio%20Labs%2C%20a%20workforce%20intelligence%20platform%2C%20studied%20company%20behavior%20across%20nearly%2022%2C000%20US%20firms.%20They%20found%20that%20companies%20making%20sustained%2C%20high-intensity%20AI%20investments%20saw%20greater%20workforce%20gains%20than%20firms%20using%20AI%20more%20lightly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20defined%20%26quot%3Bhigh-intensity%20adopters%26quot%3B%20as%20those%20who%20spent%20an%20average%20of%20about%20%2434%20a%20month%20on%20AI%2C%20compared%20to%20those%20who%20spent%20an%20average%20of%20less%20than%C2%A0%243.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHigh-intensity%20adopters%20grew%20faster.%20They%20saw%20their%20head%20count%20grow%20more%20than%2010%25%20over%20the%20first%2024%20months%20after%20adopting%20AI.%20Entry-level%20head%20count%20rose%2012%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20high-intensity%20adopters%20have%20some%20advantages.%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20larger%2C%20more%20technical%2C%20and%20faster%20growing%20before%20adoption%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20authors%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20to%20their%20success%2C%20however%2C%20is%20not%20just%20adopting%20AI%20but%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eknowing%20how%20to%20leverage%20it%20effectively.%20The%20authors%20wrote%20that%20the%20benefits%20of%20AI%20adoption%20require%20%26quot%3Bcomplementary%20investments%2C%20organizational%20change%2C%20and%20learning%20inside%20the%20firm.%26quot%3B%20In%20other%20words%2C%20a%20few%20enterprise%20chatbot%20subscriptions%20may%20not%20be%20enough%20to%20move%20the%20needle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20divide%20%E2%80%94%20between%20having%20access%20to%20AI%20and%20knowing%20how%20to%20turn%20it%20into%20value%20%E2%80%94%20shows%20up%20in%20a%20separate%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbcg-leader-says-successful-employees-have-high-agency-mindset-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBoston%20Consulting%20Group%3C%2Fa%3E%20survey%20of%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20consulting%20firm%20surveyed%20nearly%2012%2C000%20people%20for%20its%20%26quot%3BAI%20at%20Work%26quot%3B%20report%20and%20found%20that%20AI%20use%20has%20spread%20widely%3A%2074%25%20of%20frontline%20white-collar%20employees%20now%20use%20AI%20daily%20or%20several%20times%20a%20week%2C%20up%2023%25%20from%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffrontline-workers-flexibility-unions-anti-work-pto-four-day-workweek-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efrontline%20employees%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20regularly%20use%20AI%2C%20however%2C%2066%25%20of%20respondents%20said%20they've%20received%20limited%20or%20no%20guidance%20on%20how%20to%20use%20the%20time%20they%20save%2C%20and%2058%25%20said%20they%20are%20not%20reinvesting%20their%20time%20in%20more%20strategic%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBCG%20concluded%20that%20strategy%20matters%20more%20than%20tools.%20Workers%20with%20strong%20strategic%20clarity%20but%20limited%20access%20to%20AI%20tools%20reported%20greater%20measurable%20impact%20than%20those%20with%20strong%20tool%20access%20but%20little%20direction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%2080%25%20of%20respondents%20said%20they%20saw%20a%20measurable%20impact%20when%20they%20had%20a%20%26quot%3Bstrong%20strategic%20clarity%26quot%3B%20on%20how%20to%20use%20tools%2C%20even%20with%20limited%20access%20to%20them.%20Whereas%20only%2060%25%20reported%20seeing%20a%20measurable%20impact%20when%20they%20had%20limited%20strategic%20clarity%20but%20strong%20access%20to%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20enough%20to%20bring%20AI%20into%20the%20workplace%2C%20the%20reports%20found.%20It%20has%20to%20be%20done%20strategically.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-adoption-strategies-companies-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783329002000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4ab86be3bd3a50082c0637%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-adoption-strategies-companies-2026-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Realizing%20returns%20on%20AI%20adoption%20requires%20strategic%20investments%20and%20organizational%20change%2C%20two%20new%20reports%20found.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lvaranasi%40businessinsider.com%20(Lakshmi%20Varanasi)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A99%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I'm%20a%20therapist%20who%20studies%20mental%20strength.%20Here's%20the%202-minute%20power%20phrase%20strategy%20to%20keep%20you%20strong%20under%20pressure.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman's%20reflection%20in%20a%20mirror%20with%20her%20eyes%20closed%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a46d4c0e3bd3a50082bfdf6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAmy%20Morin%20(not%20pictured)%20shares%20the%20two-minute%20reset%20that%20helped%20her%20land%20a%20book%20deal.%3Cp%3EOlga%20Pankova%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAmy%20Morin%20is%20a%20psychotherapist%2C%20podcast%20host%2C%20and%20author%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpsychotherapist-shares-how-to-know-overwhelmed-vs-burned-out-work-2026-6%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estudies%20mental%20strength%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20shares%20how%20the%20two-minute%20reset%20of%20activating%20a%20power%20phrase%20can%20help%20in%20moments%20of%20pressure.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20suggests%20picking%20a%20phrase%20in%20the%20present%20tense%2C%20focused%20on%20what%20you%20can%20control%2C%20and%20stated%20positively.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202013%2C%20I%20was%20on%20a%20phone%20call%20with%20the%20editorial%20team%20at%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20publishers%20in%20the%20world%2C%20fielding%20questions%20about%20how%20I%20planned%20to%20structure%20a%20book%20I%20had%20no%20idea%20how%20to%20write.%20I%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftherapist-widowed-at-26-shares-how-she-worked-through-grief-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20full-time%20psychotherapist%3C%2Fa%3E%20who'd%20written%20a%20viral%20article%20that%20led%20to%20this%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20fumbled%20through%20a%20few%20answers%2C%20I%20caught%20myself%20thinking%2C%20%3Cem%3EDon't%20say%20anything%20stupid.%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EDon't%20blow%20this%20opportunity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20knew%20that%20thinking%20about%20all%20the%20ways%20I%20might%20mess%20up%20would%20likely%20cause%20me%20to%20mess%20up.%20So%20I%20took%20a%20deep%20breath%20and%20ran%20the%20best%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-critical-difference-between-mental-strength-and-resilience-2020-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emental%20strength%3C%2Fa%3E%20play%20I%20could%20in%20that%20moment%20%E2%80%94%20I%20activated%20my%20power%20phrase%20and%20told%20myself%2C%20%3Cem%3EI'm%20a%20strong%2C%20straightforward%20communicator.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepeating%20that%20phrase%20in%20my%20mind%20helped%20me%20field%20the%20next%20round%20of%20questions%20with%20a%20bit%20more%20poise.%20I%20shared%20my%20story%2C%20acknowledged%20I%20hadn't%20had%20much%20time%20to%20think%20about%20how%20to%20turn%20my%20ideas%20into%20a%20book%2C%20and%20assured%20them%20I%20was%20a%20hard%20worker%20and%20eager%20to%20learn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20long%20after%20that%20call%2C%20they%20made%20me%20an%20offer%2C%20and%20I%20signed%20my%20first%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-landed-six-figure-book-deal-major-publisher-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebook%20deal%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228ad0c078-0373-4eda-8683-4510a6a51955%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20two-minute%20reset%20is%20a%20way%20to%20stay%20mentally%20strong%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EActivating%20my%20power%20phrase%20was%20the%20two-minute%20mental%20reset%20that%20helped%20me%20land%20the%20book%20deal%20opportunity%2C%20and%20it's%20one%20of%2050%20tools%20for%20high-stakes%20situations%20I%20cover%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Famymorinlcsw.com%2Fthe-mental-strength-playbook%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emy%20new%20book%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Mental%20Strength%20Playbook.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThink%20about%20the%20last%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcareer-coach-shares-simple-salary-negotiation-phrase-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esalary%20negotiation%3C%2Fa%3E%20where%20you%20took%20the%20first%20number%20on%20the%20table%20or%20your%20performance%20review%20where%20you%20blanked%20on%20half%20of%20what%20you%20meant%20to%20say.%20Those%20are%20the%20moments%20a%20power%20phrase%20is%20built%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECreate%20a%20simple%20phrase%20to%20repeat%20in%20the%20two%20minutes%20between%20the%20parking%20lot%20and%20the%20room%2C%20or%20between%20sitting%20down%20at%20the%20table%20and%20being%20asked%20the%20first%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20one%20of%20the%20fastest%20ways%20to%20stay%20mentally%20strong%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20high%20the%20stakes%20are%2C%20and%20you%20can%20run%20it%20in%20the%20moment%20you%20need%20it%20most.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2275ae8d82-285d-4cc6-8e08-a8e46063d574%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20activating%20your%20power%20phrase%20works%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you're%20under%20pressure%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20you're%20trying%20to%20close%20an%20important%20deal%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmistakes-people-make-negotiating-job-offer-from-salary-negotiator-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Easking%20for%20a%20raise%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20your%20brain%20runs%20a%20default%20script.%20For%20most%20people%2C%20it%20sounds%20something%20like%2C%20%3Cem%3EI'm%20going%20to%20mess%20this%20up%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20or%2C%20%3Cem%3EThey're%20going%20to%20see%20right%20through%20me%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20power%20phrase%20%E2%80%94%20a%20short%2C%20positive%20sentence%20you%20say%20to%20yourself%20in%20the%20moment%20%E2%80%94%20interrupts%20that%20script.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Facademic.oup.com%2Fscan%2Farticle%2F11%2F4%2F621%2F2375054%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20in%20%26quot%3BSocial%20Cognitive%20and%20Affective%20Neuroscience%26quot%3B%20found%20that%20self-affirmations%20activate%20brain%20regions%20tied%20to%20self-processing%20and%20reward%2C%20which%20lead%20to%20real%20behavior%20change.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjournals.plos.org%2Fplosone%2Farticle%3Fid%3D10.1371%2Fjournal.pone.0062593%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOther%20research%3C%2Fa%3E%20shows%20that%20activating%20your%20power%20phrase%20reduces%20how%20you%20perceive%20threats%20and%20improves%20your%20performance%20under%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20conversations%20you%20have%20with%20yourself%20have%20a%20direct%20effect%20on%20how%20you%20perform%3B%20your%20body%20believes%20what%20your%20brain%20tells%20it.%20If%20you%20walk%20into%20a%20room%20telling%20yourself%2C%3Cem%3E%20I'm%20a%20horrible%20communicator%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-speak-up-at-work-communication-skills-heather-hansen-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eyour%20communication%20skills%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20reflect%20that.%20Your%20voice%20will%20be%20quieter%2C%20you'll%20avoid%20eye%20contact%2C%20and%20you%20won't%20express%20yourself%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%2C%20however%2C%20you%20walk%20in%20thinking%2C%20%3Cem%3EI%20communicate%20my%20ideas%20effectively%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20you'll%20likely%20communicate%20much%20better.%20Your%20thoughts%20about%20your%20performance%20often%20become%20a%20self-fulfilling%20prophecy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20watched%20this%20play%20out%20with%20clients%20for%20years.%20One%20was%20a%20sales%20executive%20who%20would%20freeze%20up%20before%20big%20pitches%20because%20he%20was%20convinced%20he%20was%20going%20to%20forget%20his%20talking%20points%2C%20so%20I%20helped%20him%20create%20his%20power%20phrase.%20Before%20walking%20into%20the%20room%2C%20he'd%20tell%20himself%2C%20%3Cem%3EShare%20your%20excitement.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20worked%3B%20it%20pointed%20him%20at%20the%20part%20of%20the%20job%20he%20was%20actually%20good%20at%2C%20instead%20of%20the%20part%20his%20brain%20wouldn't%20stop%20catastrophizing%20about.%20As%20his%20pitches%20improved%2C%20so%20did%20his%20close%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22eda12b96-966f-48aa-b847-f625732da39f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20activate%20your%20power%20phrase%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e5e3f09a-f533-448e-8497-abc039b2ce94%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Catch%20the%20script%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20pressure%20ramps%20up%2C%20your%20brain%20shifts%20into%20a%20default%20loop%20%E2%80%94%20usually%20some%20version%20of%20%26quot%3BI'm%20going%20to%20mess%20this%20up%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3BThey're%20going%20to%20see%20right%20through%20me.%26quot%3B%20Notice%20when%20that%20loop%20starts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224e9ec065-f695-4b71-a4d6-d0ef91597a14%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Pick%20a%20phrase%20that%20fits%20the%20moment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EA%20general%20affirmation%20like%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20enough%26quot%3B%20might%20feel%20good%20in%20the%20abstract%2C%20but%20it%20won't%20do%20much%20when%20you're%20facing%20a%20specific%20challenge.%20Match%20the%20phrase%20to%20the%20challenge%20in%20front%20of%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWalking%20into%20a%20salary%20negotiation%3F%20%26quot%3BI%20know%20my%20worth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-give-negative-feedback-to-your-boss-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egive%20difficult%20feedback%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%20%26quot%3BI%20can%20be%20direct%20and%20kind.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHeading%20into%20a%20presentation%3F%20%26quot%3BI%20communicate%20my%20ideas%20effectively.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20more%20pointed%20the%20phrase%2C%20the%20harder%20it%20works.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20three%20rules%20will%20help%20you%20pick%20a%20phrase%20that%20works%20well%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EUse%20the%20present%20tense.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20brave%26quot%3B%20works%20better%20than%20%26quot%3BI've%20done%20brave%20things.%26quot%3B%20Your%20brain%20is%20trying%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20to%20do%20right%20now.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EFocus%20on%20what%20you%20can%20control.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%26quot%3BI'm%20going%20to%20succeed%20no%20matter%20what%26quot%3B%20will%20backfire%20the%20second%20something%20goes%20sideways.%20%26quot%3BI%20can%20work%20hard%20and%20do%20my%20best%26quot%3B%20will%20help%20you%20stay%20on%20track.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EState%20it%20positively.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%26quot%3BDon't%20mess%20up%26quot%3B%20will%20make%20you%20more%20likely%20to%20mess%20up%20%E2%80%94%20your%20brain%20skips%20past%20the%20%26quot%3Bdon't%26quot%3B%20and%20locks%20onto%20%26quot%3Bmess%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22567cd4be-706f-42d9-ae67-e215e489d2cd%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Repeat%20it%20until%20the%20pressure%20passes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EA%20power%20phrase%20isn't%20a%20one-time%20statement.%20Activate%20it%20before%20you%20walk%20in%2C%20and%20keep%20running%20it%20in%20the%20background%20as%20you%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20minutes%20of%20repetition%20%E2%80%94%20before%20and%20during%20the%20moment%20%E2%80%94%20is%20usually%20enough%20to%20reset%20your%20focus.%20If%20you%20feel%20the%20default%20script%20creeping%20back%2C%20activate%20the%20power%20phrase%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERemember%2C%20you're%20not%20giving%20yourself%20a%20silent%20TED%20Talk%20%E2%80%94%20you're%20just%20repeating%20your%20power%20phrase%20louder%20than%20the%20script%20your%20brain%20wants%20to%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famy-morin-mental-strength-two-minute-reset-power-phrase-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783329001000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a46d6871bba93485607b1db%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famy-morin-mental-strength-two-minute-reset-power-phrase-2026-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20psychotherapist%20who%20studies%20mental%20strength%20shares%20how%20a%20two-minute%20power%20phrase%20strategy%20can%20help%20in%20high-pressure%20situations.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Amy%20Morin)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Two%20Men%20Drown%20At%20Navi%20Mumbai%20Dam%20Complex%20As%20Heavy%20Rain%20Swells%20Water%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22So%20far%2C%20the%20body%20of%20one%20person%20has%20been%20recovered%2C%20while%20a%20police%20search%20operation%20is%20underway%20for%20the%20other.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783328919000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2026-07%2Fliik6df4_dam_625x300_06_July_26.png%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1280%2Cheight%3D720%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaharashtra-monsoon-two-men-drown-at-navi-mumbai-dam-complex-as-heavy-rain-swells-water-11732937%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22So%20far%2C%20the%20body%20of%20one%20person%20has%20been%20recovered%2C%20while%20a%20police%20search%20operation%20is%20underway%20for%20the%20other.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaharashtra-monsoon-two-men-drown-at-navi-mumbai-dam-complex-as-heavy-rain-swells-water-11732937%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaharashtra-monsoon-two-men-drown-at-navi-mumbai-dam-complex-as-heavy-rain-swells-water-11732937%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaharashtra-monsoon-two-men-drown-at-navi-mumbai-dam-complex-as-heavy-rain-swells-water-11732937%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20top%20Booking.com%20exec%20shares%20his%20go-to%20AI%20prompt%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224134%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Booking.com%20chief%20business%20officer%20James%20Waters%20wears%20a%20light%20blue%20button-up%20shirt%20and%20leans%20on%20a%20rooftop%20railing%20with%20a%20blurred%20city%20backdrop.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4672431aaffe3020cb2990%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222756%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBooking.com%20chief%20business%20officer%20James%20Waters.%3Cp%3EBooking.com%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBooking.com's%20chief%20business%20officer%20said%20he%20uses%20AI%20to%20analyze%20how%20rivals%20are%20tackling%20strategic%20problems.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EJames%20Waters%2C%20who%20oversees%20areas%20like%20product%2C%20said%20AI%20helps%20with%20research%20that%20would%20otherwise%20take%20days.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20company%20is%20also%20tracking%20AI%20spending%20and%20working%20to%20give%20teams%20greater%20visibility%20into%20token%20usage.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBooking.com's%20James%20Waters%20has%20a%20new%20team%20for%20opposition%20research%C2%A0%E2%80%94%20their%20names%20are%20Claude%2C%20Gemini%2C%20and%20ChatGPT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20online%20travel%20giant's%20chief%20business%20officer%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20one%20of%20his%20favorite%20AI%20prompts%20is%20essentially%20for%20competitive%20analysis.%20He%20said%20he%20asks%20AI%20models%20to%20break%20down%20how%20rivals%2C%20digital%20platforms%2C%20and%20technology%20companies%20tackle%20major%20strategic%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20for%20me%20is%20super%20powerful%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bbecause%20I%20could%20theoretically%20do%20that%20research%20myself%2C%20but%20it%20would%20take%20days.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20he%20used%20Anthropic's%20Claude%20to%20look%20at%20customer%20reviews%20%E2%80%94%20from%20how%20they're%20displayed%20on%20other%20platforms%20to%20how%20they're%20summarized%20and%20weighted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20kind%20of%20research%20is%20where%20AI%20is%20especially%20useful%20for%20me%3A%20it%20helps%20synthesize%20a%20broad%20strategic%20landscape%20in%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20time%2C%20and%20then%20I%20can%20dig%20deeper%20where%20needed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20travel%20industry%2C%20like%20many%20others%2C%20is%20being%20reshaped%20by%20AI%2C%20both%20in%20how%20travelers%20discover%20travel%20sites%20and%20how%20those%20companies%20operate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBooking.com%20has%20rolled%20out%20AI%20agents%20to%20help%20customers%20research%20and%20plan%20trips%2C%20and%20is%20expanding%20and%20personalizing%20those%20as%20part%20of%20its%20Connected%20Trip%20strategy.%20It%20also%20works%20with%20OpenAI%2C%20Anthropic%2C%20Google%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20and%20Amazon%20on%20AI%20tools%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eincluding%20AI%20Trip%20Planner%20with%20OpenAI%20and%20a%20partnership%20with%20Anthropic%20that%20lets%20Claude%20users%20book%20travel%20directly%20within%20conversations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220b6328d4-122c-46e0-a9e0-4d5998a643c8%5C%22%3EHow%20Booking.com%20is%20trying%20to%20solve%20the%20AI%20budgeting%20problem%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWaters%2C%20who%20oversees%20product%20development%2C%20marketing%2C%20customer%20service%2C%20commercial%20operations%2C%20and%20technology%2C%20said%20AI's%20biggest%20impact%20has%20been%20on%20engineering%2C%20where%20developers%20are%20writing%20more%20code.%20HR%20and%20finance%20teams%20are%20also%20using%20tools%20like%20Claude%20Code%20for%20forecasting%20and%20financial%20analysis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20culture%20is%20adjusting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCulturally%2C%20you're%20trying%20to%20create%20this%20balance%20of%2080%25%20excitement%20about%20the%20possibilities%20that%20are%20there%20that%20didn't%20used%20to%20be%20there%2C%20and%2020%25%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20fear%20of%2C%20look%2C%20if%20we%20get%20this%20wrong%2C%20someone%20else%20takes%20our%20customers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20many%20companies%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3Fh%3D2fb8b0d7e1b540865d908bfe0c87c44b688f237f99471a4b31e776dc60bc8702%26postID%3D6a3d5e10f9367a0a3d122e58%26postSlug%3Dbooking-com-top-exec-shares-go-to-ai-prompt-2026-7%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fbooking.com%252F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBooking.com%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20also%20watching%20its%20AI%20spending.%20Uber%20execs%20recently%20said%20the%20company%20blew%20through%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-coo-andrew-macdonald-ai-token-spending-harder-justify-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EClaude%20Code%20budget%20for%202026%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20that%20it's%20getting%20harder%20to%20justify%20token%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWaters%20said%20Booking.com%20measures%20its%20total%20investment%20in%20tokens%20and%20people%20across%20the%20value%20they%20generate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20it%20matters%20if%20you%20spend%20a%20whole%20load%20of%20money%20on%20tokens%20and%20far%20more%20than%20you%20plan%2C%20because%20you're%20generating%20way%20more%20value%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20funnel%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20problem%20is%2C%20if%20those%20two%20things%20don't%20run%20together.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20tracks%20where%20tokens%20are%20spent%20and%20when%20cheaper%20models%20can%20be%20used%20for%20simpler%20tasks.%20Now%2C%20it's%20thinking%20about%20how%20to%20give%20product%20teams%20better%20visibility%20into%20what%20they're%20spending%20and%20bringing%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20definitely%20in%20our%20mind%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20this%20is%20a%20fear%20for%20us%20at%20this%20moment%20in%20life%20that%20this%20gets%20out%20of%20control.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20Waters%2C%20the%20problem%20isn't%20much%20different%20than%20managing%20cloud%20spending%20was%2012%20or%2018%20months%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20the%20scale%20of%20spend%20will%20go%20up%20much%20quicker%20if%20you%20don't%20do%20it%20in%20a%20sensible%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbooking-com-top-exec-shares-go-to-ai-prompt-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783328821000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a46a80ce3bd3a50082bfb65%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbooking-com-top-exec-shares-go-to-ai-prompt-2026-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Booking.com's%20chief%20business%20officer%20James%20Waters%20describes%20his%20use%20of%20AI%20to%20analyze%20strategic%20problems%20%E2%80%94%20and%20how%20he%20tracks%20token%20spending.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22arodriguez%40businessinsider.com%20(Ashley%20Rodriguez)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Meet%20the%20MAGA%20darling%20mobilizing%20Americans%20against%20Big%20AI%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223445%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Amy%20Kremer%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a41709e360acd489560ca82%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222297%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAmy%20Kremer%20is%20the%20cofounder%20of%20Women%20for%20Trump%20and%20Women%20for%20America%20First.%20Now%20she's%20taking%20on%20AI%20data%20centers.%3Cp%3EJacquelyn%20Martin%2FAP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAmy%20Kremer%20is%20chair%20of%20Humans%20First%2C%20a%20nonprofit%20pushing%20an%20%26quot%3BAmerica%20First%26quot%3B%20approach%20to%20AI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHumans%20First%20is%20hosting%20a%20nationwide%20protest%20against%20data%20centers%20on%20July%2018.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EKremer%20was%20also%20a%20key%20organizer%20of%20the%20January%206%20rally%20in%202021.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjan-6-rally-organizer-wanted-stop-obama-2009-certification-report-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAmy%20Kremer%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20worn%20many%20hats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe's%20been%20a%20flight%20attendant.%20She's%20participated%20in%20the%20Republican%20National%20Committee.%20She's%20a%20Women%20for%20Trump%20and%20Women%20for%20America%20First%20cofounder.%20And%20she%20was%20a%20%26quot%3BStop%20the%20Steal%26quot%3B%20supporter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20most%20notably%2C%20she%20was%20one%20of%20the%20primary%20organizers%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjanuary-6-rally-organizers-burner-phones-trump-team-communications-ellipse-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJanuary%206%20rally%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20in%202021%2C%20which%20spiraled%20into%20a%20riot%20at%20the%20US%20Capitol.%20She%20did%20not%20plan%20or%20participate%20in%20that%20part.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%20a%20former%20Tea%20Party%20member%2C%20she%20has%20been%20at%20the%20center%20of%20many%20of%20the%20most%20recognizable%20conservative%20movements%20of%20the%20past%2017%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20she's%20rallying%20Americans%20against%20a%20new%20cause%3A%20Big%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20this%20is%20the%20most%20important%20fight%20of%20our%20lifetime%2C%26quot%3B%20Kremer%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThis%20technology%20could%20wipe%20us%20off%20the%20face%20of%20the%20planet.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKremer%20is%20now%20the%20chair%20of%20Humans%20First%2C%20a%20nonprofit%20working%20to%20give%20Americans%20a%20greater%20voice%20in%20AI%20policy.%20The%20group%2C%20founded%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20is%20organizing%20a%20nationwide%20protest%20against%20AI%20data%20centers%20on%20July%2018.%20So%20far%2C%20the%20group%20has%20planned%20demonstrations%20in%2022%20US%20states%2C%20including%2011%20in%20Texas%20and%20seven%20in%20Florida.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20doing%20this%20because%20the%20people%20of%20this%20country%20are%20rising%20up%20and%20saying%2C%20'We%20don't%20want%20these%20hyperscale%20data%20centers%20in%20our%20communities%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a372efb0-b55d-4d4a-a2dd-491e22bb32c2%5C%22%3EThe%20anti-data%20center%20movement%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20needs%20data%20centers%20like%20humans%20need%20oxygen.%20Companies%20like%20OpenAI%2C%20Anthropic%2C%20Google%2C%20and%20Meta%20require%20ever-increasing%20compute%20to%20train%20and%20operate%20their%20products.%20That%20compute%20is%20generated%20by%20the%20servers%20and%20processors%20housed%20in%20data%20centers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithout%20these%20massive%20data%20centers%2C%20advancements%20in%20artificial%20intelligence%20could%20stall%2C%20threatening%20bottom%20lines%20and%20investor%20tolerance.%20It%20would%20also%20benefit%20China%2C%20the%20United%20States'%20biggest%20competitor%20in%20the%20race%20to%20dominate%20the%20AI%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20these%20reasons%20and%20more%2C%20many%20industrial-minded%20Americans%20support%20the%20rapid%20construction%20of%20hyperscale%20data%20centers.%20Beyond%20their%20necessity%20to%20run%20the%20AI%20race%2C%20supporters%20say%20they%20encourage%20economic%20growth%20in%20the%20communities%20where%20they%20are%20built%20and%20create%20jobs%20for%20locals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BData%20centers%20are%20vital%20to%20enabling%20emerging%20technologies%20like%20AI%2C%20which%20are%20critical%20to%20US%20national%20security%20and%20global%20economic%20competitiveness%2C%26quot%3B%20Josh%20Levi%2C%20president%20of%20the%20Data%20Center%20Coalition%2C%20an%20association%20that%20supports%20the%20data%20center%20industry%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELocals%2C%20however%2C%20worry%20that%20the%20data%20centers%20powering%20AI%20will%20raise%20their%20electricity%20bills%2C%20worsen%20the%20environment%2C%20and%20generally%20degrade%20the%20quality%20of%20life%20in%20the%20rural%20communities%20where%20they%20are%20typically%20built.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20them%20also%20just%20don't%20like%20AI.%20Although%20data%20centers%20aren't%20new%2C%20the%20massive%20versions%20needed%20to%20make%20AI%20work%20have%20become%2C%20for%20many%20Americans%2C%20the%20tangible%20symbol%20of%20their%20dislike%20for%20the%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20proving%20to%20be%20a%20bipartisan%20issue.%20Data%20centers%20are%20uniting%20Americans%20across%20blue%20and%20red%20states%20like%20few%20other%20issues%2C%20and%20they%20are%20expected%20to%20play%20a%20role%20in%20the%20coming%20midterm%20elections.%20A%20Gallup%20poll%20published%20in%20May%20found%20that%20over%2070%25%20of%20surveyed%20Americans%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgallup-opposition-data-centers-nuclear-reactors-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edon't%20want%20a%20data%20center%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20their%20backyard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-data-center-near-me-location-tracker-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E1%2C400%20data%20centers%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20already%20been%20built%20or%20approved%20for%20construction%20by%20the%20end%20of%202025%2C%20with%20hundreds%20more%20in%20the%20works.%20Many%20towns%20and%20cities%20have%20paused%20construction%20of%20data%20centers.%20Some%20have%20outright%20banned%20them%20entirely.%20Democratic%20Reps.%20Bernie%20Sanders%20and%20Alexandria%20Ocasio-Cortez%20have%20called%20for%20a%20federal%20moratorium.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Kremer%20shares%20their%20concerns%2C%20she%20doesn't%20share%20their%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20do%20not%20believe%20in%20a%20nationwide%20moratorium%20or%20even%20a%20statewide%20moratorium.%20We%20believe%20that%20each%20community%20should%20have%20a%20choice%20in%20what%20they%20put%20in%20their%20community%2C%26quot%3B%20Kremer%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20that's%20not%20happening%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20places.%20It's%20being%20done%20behind%20closed%20doors.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226682%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Data%20Center%20Protest%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1b2419b4fb977f359826d3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224455%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUtah%20residents%20protest%20the%20Stratos%20Project%2C%20a%20data%20center%20campus%20backed%20by%20Kevin%20O'Leary%2C%20outside%20the%20Utah%20State%20Capitol%20in%20May.%3Cp%3ENatalie%20Behring%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22921f1d2e-5d94-4385-a33d-5c9335fdab67%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20data%20centers%20became%20her%20next%20target%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKremer%20said%20data%20centers%20first%20came%20to%20her%20attention%20in%202024%2C%20when%20videos%20of%20communities%20opposing%20their%20development%20began%20spreading%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20a%20techie%2C%20so%20I%20didn't%20realize%20the%20connection%20to%20data%20centers%20and%20AI%20at%20the%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20learned%20that%20the%20data%20centers%20are%20the%20backbone%20and%20infrastructure%20of%20AI.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20learned%20that%20parents%20had%20accused%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-add-chatgpt-safeguards-teen-suicide-lawsuit-ai-mental-health-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20chatbots%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20contributing%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-character-ai-settling-lawsuits-teen-suicides-new-york-texas-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eteen%20suicides%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20that%20lawsuits%20had%20accused%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-states-investigation-chatgpt-impact-children-vulnerable-adults-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenAI's%20ChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20having%20a%20role%20in%20a%20shooting.%20Bleak%20forecasts%20that%20AI%20could%20take%20over%20traditional%20human%20jobs%20weren't%20comforting%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20technology%20has%20been%20built%20on%20American%20data%20with%20American%20taxpayer%20dollars%20invested%20into%20these%20companies%20with%20American%20energy%20and%20American%20land%2C%26quot%3B%20Kremer%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20no%20voice%20in%20how%20the%20technology%20is%20used%20or%20how%20it%20impacts%20our%20lives%2C%20and%20that's%20not%20right.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKremer%20said%20she%20isn't%20anti-tech%2C%20but%20agrees%20with%20Americans%20who%20want%20to%20implement%20guardrails%20around%20frontier%20AI%20systems.%20She%20also%20believes%20data%20center%20developers%20and%20local%20governments%20should%20be%20transparent%20with%20residents%20about%20the%20full%20parameters%20of%20each%20project%2C%20and%20give%20residents%20a%20real%20chance%20to%20weigh%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Protests%20against%20data%20centers%20in%20Michigan.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a418019360acd489560cae9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMichigan%20residents%20protest%20a%20data%20center%20in%20December%202025.%3Cp%3EUCG%2FUCG%2FUniversal%20Images%20Group%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20reality%20is%20these%20companies%20have%20more%20money%20than%20God%2C%26quot%3B%20Kremer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20guarantee%20you%20that%20when%20Republicans%20are%20no%20longer%20controlling%20all%20the%20chambers%2C%20they're%20going%20to%20be%20cozying%20up%20to%20the%20Democrats%20because%2C%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20all%20they%20care%20about%20is%20power%20and%20control%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKremer%20said%20she%20also%20blames%20the%20federal%20government%2C%20though%20not%20Trump%2C%20who%20has%20made%20supporting%20America's%20AI%20ambitions%20a%20central%20part%20of%20his%20agenda.%20His%20administration%20accelerated%20federal%20permitting%20and%20backed%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foracle-openai-stargate-loans-jpmorgan-diminishing-interest-debt-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EStargate%20Project%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20%24500%20billion%20effort%20to%20build%20huge%20data%20centers%20to%20power%20AI.%20In%20May%2C%20Trump%20delayed%20signing%20an%20executive%20order%20on%20AI%20guardrails%20over%20fears%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-signs-scaled-back-ai-executive-order-anthropic-mythos-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efalling%20behind%20China%3C%2Fa%3E.%20His%20administration%2C%20however%2C%20did%20just%20briefly%20table%20Anthropic's%20latest%20models%2C%20Mythos%20and%20Fable%2C%20over%20security%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20Congress's%20responsibility%2C%20and%20they%20need%20to%20get%20their%20act%20together%20and%20listen%20to%20and%20protect%20the%20American%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BPresident%20Trump's%20executive%20orders%2C%20and%20his%20most%20recent%20executive%20order%20on%20testing%20frontier%20AI%20systems%2C%20need%20to%20go%20further.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUntil%20then%2C%20however%2C%20Kremer%20said%20she'd%20be%20among%20those%20leading%20the%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20a%20parent%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20know%20no%20parent%20anywhere%20that%20would%20ever%20say%2C%20'My%20child's%20in%20danger.%20I'm%20going%20to%20wait%20on%20Congress%20to%20act.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famy-kremer-humans-first-ai-data-center-nationwide-protest-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783328701000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a417155e218c3b62535e6e8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famy-kremer-humans-first-ai-data-center-nationwide-protest-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amy%20Kremer%20was%20a%20%26quot%3BStop%20the%20Steal%26quot%3B%20activist%20who%20helped%20organize%20the%20January%206%20rally%20in%202021.%20She's%20now%20mobilizing%20against%20AI%20data%20centers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ledmonds%40businessinsider.com%20(Lauren%20Edmonds)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22George%20Clooney%20to%20Be%20Honored%20at%20Venice%20Film%20Festival%20With%20Golden%20Lion%20for%20Career%20Achievement%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783328554000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236802227%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Venice%20Film%20Festival%20will%20honor%20George%20Clooney%20with%20its%202026%20Golden%20Lion%20for%20Lifetime%20Achievement.%20Clooney%20%E2%80%93%20who%20is%20one%20of%20only%20three%20people%20to%20have%20been%20nominated%20in%20six%20different%20Oscar%20categories%20throughout%20his%20career%20(best%20picture%2C%20director%2C%20lead%20actor%2C%20supporting%20actor%2C%20original%20screenplay%20and%20adapted%20screenplay)%20%E2%80%93%20will%20be%20celebrated%20on%20the%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Nvivarelli%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Where%20to%20invest%20%2410%2C000%20right%20now%2C%20acco