%2C%20international%20stocks%2C%20mid%20caps%2C%20industrials%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJames%20McCann%2C%20senior%20economist%20at%20Edward%20Jones%2C%20says%20to%20look%20outside%20mega-cap%20tech%2C%20and%20notes%20that%20EM%20equities%20have%20already%20been%20outperforming%20this%20year%20amid%20strong%20earnings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20iShares%20MSCI%20Emerging%20Markets%20ETF%2C%20one%20fund%20that%20offers%20exposure%20to%20EM%20companies%2C%20is%20up%20roughly%2020%25%20year%20to%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcCann%20doesn't%20say%20to%20get%20out%20of%20tech%20entirely%20%E2%80%94%20just%20look%20overseas%2C%20as%20well%20as%20at%20mid-cap%20stocks%20and%20industrials%2C%20which%20offer%20exposure%20without%20directly%20buying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20says%20industrials%20are%20actually%20his%20team's%20favorite%20sector%20call%20right%20now%2C%20citing%20a%20new%20cycle%20beginning%20amid%20higher%20oil%20prices%20and%20strengthening%20manufacturing%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20funds%20offering%20exposure%20to%20this%20area%20is%20the%20Industrial%20Select%20Sector%20SPDR%20Fund%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fetfs%2Fstate-street-industrial-select-sector-spdr-etf-us81369y7040%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EXLI%3C%2Fa%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EJose%20Rasco%2C%20CIO%20at%20HSBC%20Wealth%20Management%20%26amp%3B%20Private%20Bank%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225120%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20HSBC%20Holdings%20Plc%20offices%20in%20the%20Canary%20Wharf%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a46a1ae65e65d39ff1c914a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223408%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBloomberg%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EInvesting%20ideas%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Utilities%2C%20industrials%2C%20value%20stocks%2C%20US%20Treasurys%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERasco%20said%20he%20remains%20bullish%20on%20equities%20and%20would%20put%20most%20of%20the%20%2410%2C000%20into%20strategic%20areas%20of%20the%20stock%20market.%20He%20sees%20particular%20opportunity%20in%20utilities%20and%20in%20industrials%2C%20which%20stand%20to%20benefit%20from%20the%20AI%20buildout.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERasco%20said%20he%20would%20also%20hunt%20for%20good%20deals%20in%20the%20market%2C%20pointing%20to%20how%20value%20stocks%20have%20started%20to%20pull%20ahead%20of%20growth%20stocks%20in%20recent%20months.%20The%20Vanguard%20Value%20Index%20Fund%2C%20one%20fund%20that%20offers%20exposure%20to%20those%20companies%2C%20is%20up%2013%25%20for%20the%20year%2C%20compared%20to%20the%206%25%20year-to-date%20gain%20in%20the%20Vanguard%20Growth%20Index%20Fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20Rasco%20adds%20that%20he%20would%20also%20allocate%20a%20small%20position%20to%20US%20government%20bonds.%20Assuming%20that%20inflation%20cools%20and%20rates%20eventually%20come%20down%2C%20Treasurys%20could%20appreciate%20in%20value%2C%20which%20he%20said%20was%20an%20opportunity%20for%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFunds%20offering%20exposure%20to%20these%20areas%20include%20the%20Utilities%20Select%20Sector%20SPDR%20Fund%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fetfs%2Fstate-street-utilities-select-sector-spdr-etf-us81369y8865%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EXLU%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20the%20Vanguard%20Industrials%20ETF%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fetfs%2Fvanguard-industrials-index-fund-etf-shares-us92204a6038%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EVIS%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20and%20the%20iShares%2020%2B%20Year%20Treasury%20Bond%20ETF%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fetfs%2Fishares-20-year-treasury-bond-etf-us4642874329%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETLT%3C%2Fa%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhere-to-invest-10000-right-now-ai-trade-iran-warsh-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E