ECelebrity%20stylist%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flaw-roach-joined-forces-with-zendaya-promised-elevate-each-other-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELaw%20Roach%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20working%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fceline-dion-most-daring-looks-photos%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECeline%20Dion%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20a%20lasting%20impact%20on%20his%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20Celine%20actually%20made%20me%20so%20much%20of%20a%20better%20stylist%2C%26quot%3B%20Roach%20told%20The%20Daily%20Beast's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DhSfgMQZ5W8E%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BObsessed%26quot%3B%20podcast.%3C%2Fa%3E%20After%20styling%20younger%20stars%20like%20Zendaya%20and%20Ariana%20Grande%2C%20Roach%20said%20that%20dressing%20the%20Canadian%20pop%20icon%20pushed%20him%20to%20become%20more%20detail-oriented.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20talking%20about%20working%20with%20two%20girls%20who%20were%20very%20new%20to%20the%20industry%2C%20right%3F%20To%20go%20and%20work%20with%20someone%20who%20was%20a%2030-year%20vet%20at%20that%20time%2C%20it's%20a%20different%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20Roach%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoach%20recalled%20their%20first%20fitting%20together%2C%20when%20Dion%20quickly%20identified%20every%20adjustment%20she%20wanted%20made%20to%20a%20gown%20before%20asking%20for%20his%20thoughts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20kind%20of%20stuck%20because%20I'm%20watching%20her%20see%20all%20the%20imperfections%2C%20and%20I%20didn't%20see%20anything%20that%20she%20didn't%20see%2C%26quot%3B%20Roach%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20their%20next%20fitting%2C%20he%20made%20it%20his%20goal%20to%20spot%20every%20adjustment%20that%20the%20garment%20needed%20before%20Dion%20did%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20challenged%20me%20to%20be%20better%20because%20had%20I%20not%20been%20able%20to%20do%20that%2C%20what%20value%20was%20I%20adding%3F%26quot%3B%20Roach%20said.%20The%20experience%20sharpened%20his%20eye%20and%20made%20him%20more%20discerning%20%E2%80%94%20skills%20that%20still%20shape%20the%20way%20he%20works%20with%20clients%20today%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20wasn't%20the%20only%20lesson%20Roach%20says%20he%20took%20away%20from%20working%20with%20Dion%2C%20Roach%20said.%20He%20recalled%20rushing%20to%20fasten%20one%20of%20the%20singer's%20shoes%20before%20an%20event%20and%20struggling%20with%20the%20buckle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20said%2C%20'Take%20your%20time.%20It%20goes%20faster%2C'%26quot%3B%20Roach%20said%2C%20recounting%20Dion's%20words.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20taught%20him%20the%20importance%20of%20treating%20everyone%20with%20kindness%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20go%20places%20with%20Celine%2C%20and%20she%20would%20stop%20and%20say%20hello%20to%20every%20single%20person%20and%20introduce%20herself%2C%26quot%3B%20Roach%20said.%20%26quot%3BShe'll%20introduce%20herself%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20whatever%20we're%20doing%2C%20and%20at%20the%20end%20she'll%20say%20goodbye%20and%20thank%20you%20to%20everyone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20it%20%26quot%3Bmeans%20so%20much%26quot%3B%20for%20people%20to%20be%20acknowledged%20by%20someone%20of%20Dion's%20stature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoach%20first%20started%20styling%20Dion%20in%202016%2C%20months%20after%20the%20singer%20lost%20her%20husband%2C%20Ren%C3%A9%20Ang%C3%A9lil%2C%20to%20throat%20cancer.%20Dion%20reached%20out%20after%20seeing%20his%20work%20with%20Zendaya%2C%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpeople.com%2Fstyle%2Fceline-dions-new-stylist-says-the-singers-really-enjoying-herself-through-fashion-after-very-tough-year%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20People%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20July%20of%20that%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20liked%20that%20%5BZendaya's%20style%5D%20had%20some%20sophistication%20to%20it%2C%20and%20she%20liked%20it%2C%20so%20she%20Googled%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Roach%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pair%20have%20stayed%20in%20touch%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20Roach%20announced%20on%20Instagram%20that%20he%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flaw-roach-zendaya-stylist-retirement-announcement-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eretiring%20from%20celebrity%20styling%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20%26quot%3Bthe%20politics%2C%20the%20lies%20and%20false%20narratives%20finally%20got%20me.%26quot%3B%20However%2C%20he%20came%20out%20of%20retirement%20the%20following%20year%20to%20style%20Dion%20for%20her%20surprise%20appearance%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaylor-swift-celine-dion-controversy-backlash-explained-grammys-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E66th%20Grammy%20Awards%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Dion%20has%20kept%20a%20relatively%20low%20profile%20since%20announcing%20her%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fcline-dion-stiff-person-syndrome-symptoms-causes-of-rare-disease-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Estiff-person%20syndrome%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20diagnosis%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fceline-dion-stiff-person-syndrome-neurological-disorder-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDecember%202022.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flaw-roach-working-with-celine-dion-better-at-job-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783326355000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4b1c0ce3bd3a50082c06dd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flaw-roach-working-with-celine-dion-better-at-job-2026-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%202024%2C%20Law%20Roach%20came%20out%20of%20retirement%20to%20style%20Celine%20Dion%20for%20h