publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmeghalaya-seeks-relaxations-in-foreign-funding-rules-for-schools-hospitals-11732590%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmeghalaya-seeks-relaxations-in-foreign-funding-rules-for-schools-hospitals-11732590%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fast%20food's%20newest%20rival%20isn't%20another%20burger%20chain.%20It's%20the%20grocery%20store.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20quick-grab%20section%20of%20a%20deli%20or%20grocery%20store%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a458d352680585ce91a369d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222533%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAs%20value-seeking%20behaviors%20among%20consumers%20intensify%2C%20the%20grocery%20store%20deli%20aisle%20is%20giving%20fast%20food%20chains%20a%20run%20for%20their%20money.%3Cp%3EJeffrey%20Greenberg%2FEducation%20Images%2FUniversal%20Images%20Group%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EFast-food%20chains%20are%20competing%20with%20grocery%20stores%20offering%20prepared%20meals%20to%20value-seeking%20diners.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHigh%20fast-food%20prices%20have%20narrowed%20the%20cost%20gap%20with%20grocery%20prepared%20foods%2C%20boosting%20their%20appeal.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGrocery%20stores%20are%20doubling%20down%20on%20prepared%20foods%2C%20such%20as%20hot%20bars%20and%20deli%20cases.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20years%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdiners-fast-food-vs-fast-casual-shake-shack-chickfila-loyalty-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efast-food%20chains%3C%2Fa%3E%20fought%20to%20steal%20customers%20from%20one%20another.%20Increasingly%2C%20their%20biggest%20competition%20may%20be%20coming%20from%20the%20grocery%20aisle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20inflation-weary%20consumers%20rethink%20what%20counts%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerica-k-shaped-economy-breaking-fast-food-playbook-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egood%20value%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20supermarkets'%20expanding%20prepared-food%20offerings%20are%20becoming%20a%20viable%20alternative%20to%20a%20drive-thru%20meal.%20New%20foot-traffic%20data%20from%20location%20analytics%20firm%20Placer.ai%20suggests%20that%20the%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Eshift%20is%20beginning%20to%20show%20up%20in%20Americans'%20choices%20about%20where%20to%20eat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERestaurant%20traffic%20has%20softened%20overall%20this%20year%2C%20but%20the%20pain%20hasn't%20been%20evenly%20distributed.%20Quick-service%20restaurants%20have%20struggled%20while%20fast-casual%20chains%2C%20casual%20dining%20restaurants%2C%20and%20fine%20dining%20have%20proved%20more%20resilient.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20reason%20is%20that%20grocery%20stores%20and%20superstores%20are%20increasingly%20competing%20for%20the%20same%20dining%20occasions%20with%20ready-to-eat%20meals%20that%20offer%20a%20similar%20mix%20of%20convenience%20at%20a%20lower%20perceived%20cost%2C%20according%20to%20Placer.ai.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRestaurant%20chains%20across%20all%20tiers%20are%20navigating%20mounting%20macroeconomic%20and%20competitive%20pressures%20in%202026%2C%20as%20rising%20menu%20prices%20weaken%20traditional%20value%20perceptions%20and%20consumers%20increasingly%20substitute%20grocery%20and%20other%20food-at-home%20alternatives%2C%26quot%3B%20R.J.%20Hottovy%2C%20Placer.ai's%20head%20of%20analytical%20research%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cf112ba5-0736-4b31-8853-9edc02119807%5C%22%3EGrocery%20chains%20are%20doubling%20down%20on%20grab-and-go%20meals%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20findings%20reinforce%20a%20broader%20trend%20already%20taking%20shape%20across%20the%20grocery%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERetailers%20from%20Kroger%20to%20Whole%20Foods%20have%20invested%20heavily%20in%20prepared%20foods%2C%20while%20warehouse%20clubs%20and%20mass%20merchants%20have%20expanded%20grab-and-go%20meals%2C%20sushi%20counters%2C%20hot%20bars%2C%20and%20other%20ready-to-eat%20options%20to%20capture%20more%20of%20consumers'%20food%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrocery-store-ready-to-eat-replacing-restaurants-trends-competition-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGrocery%20store%3C%2Fa%3E%20executives%20have%20increasingly%20described%20prepared%20foods%20as%20a%20growth%20opportunity%20as%20shoppers%20seek%20restaurant-quality%20meals%20without%20restaurant%20prices%2C%20Business%20Insider%20reported%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shift%20also%20reflects%20how%20consumers%20define%20value.%20Rather%20than%20simply%20looking%20for%20the%20cheapest%20meal%2C%20diners%20are%20weighing%20convenience%2C%20quality%2C%20and%20experience%20alongside%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHottovy%20said%20visitation%20data%20confirms%20%26quot%3Bseveral%20success%20stories%20across%20the%20industry%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20particularly%20fast-casual%20chains%20that%20combine%20value%2C%20menu%20innovation%2C%20and%20strong%20operations%2C%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchipotle-cava-thriving-consumers-prioritize-value-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EChipotle%20and%20Cava%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20while%20the%20QSR%20segment%20has%20reported%20lower%20foot%20traffic%20over%20four%20of%20the%20last%20five%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYears%20of%20menu%20price%20increases%20at%20fast-food%20chains%20have%20narrowed%20the%20cost%20gap%20between%20quick-service%20restaurants%20and%20both%20grocery%20prepared%20foods%20and%20fast-casual%20chains%2C%20making%20those%20alternatives%20more%20attractive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsumer%20research%20from%20Technomic%2C%20a%20consumer%20insights%20company%2C%20points%20in%20the%20same%20direction.%2070%25%20of%20consumers%20surveyed%20said%20groceries%20prepared%20at%20home%20provide%20the%20best%20value%20for%20their%20money.%20Retail-prepared%20foods%20and%20restaurant%20meals%20were%20closely%20tied%2C%20with%2016%25%20of%20respondents%20choosing%20prepared%20foods%20and%2015%25%20choosing%20restaurants%20%E2%80%94%20a%20sign%20that%20consumers%20increasingly%20see%20grocery%20stores%20as%20a%20compelling%20alternative%20to%20eating%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20recent%20earnings%20calls%2C%20McDonald's%20executives%20said%20the%20company%20is%20leaning%20into%20its%20McValue%20platform%20and%20affordability%20to%20win%20over%20cost-conscious%20diners%2C%20while%20Yum%20Brands%20highlighted%20Taco%20Bell's%20value%20offerings%20and%20menu%20innovation%20as%20key%20drivers%20of%20traffic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20emphasized%20giving%20consumers%20more%20reasons%20to%20choose%20restaurants%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-economy-warning-sign-household-debt-consumer-spending-savings-stocks-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehousehold%20budgets%3C%2Fa%3E%20remain%20under%20pressure.%20That%20helps%20explain%20why%20nearly%20every%20major%20fast-food%20chain%20has%20spent%20the%20past%20year%20talking%20up%20value%3A%20consumers%20aren't%20only%20weighing%20one%20restaurant%20against%20another%20anymore%3B%20they're%20weighing%20it%20against%20what's%20for%20dinner%20at%20the%20grocery%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffast-food-chains-face-growing-competition-from-grocery-stores-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783321861000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a458d5cec11c5f7e7fa7678%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffast-food-chains-face-growing-competition-from-grocery-stores-2026-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Fast-food%20chains%20face%20new%20competition%20as%20gro