e%20recent%20turmoil%20hasn't%20changed%20its%20bullish%20outlook.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESouth%20Korea%20was%20Asia's%20best-performing%20equity%20market%20in%20the%20first%20half%20of%202026%2C%20with%20the%20benchmark%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Findex%2Fkospi%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKospi%20index%3C%2Fa%3E%20nearly%20doubling.%20But%20that%20rally%20came%20under%20pressure%20recently%2C%20with%20sharp%20swings%20in%20chip%20stocks%20triggering%20circuit%20breakers%20and%20testing%20investor%20appetite.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20the%20Kospi%20opened%20higher%20before%20reversing%20course%20to%20close%200.5%25%20in%20the%20red.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20concerns%20about%20concentration%20risk%20%E2%80%94%20as%20AI-driven%20gains%20in%20Samsung%20Electronics%20and%20SK%20Hynix%20drove%20most%20of%20the%20market's%20gain%20%E2%80%94%20Goldman%20expects%20the%20rally%20to%20broaden%20beyond%20the%20AI%20memory-chip%20trade%20in%20the%20second%20half.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEarnings%20momentum%20is%20increasingly%20improving%20across%20other%20sectors%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20analysts%20at%20Goldman%20in%20a%20note%20on%20Sunday%2C%20pointing%20to%20energy%2C%20materials%20and%20industrials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shift%20is%20showing%20up%20in%20investor%20positioning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIncremental%20foreign%20inflows%20have%20already%20begun%20rotating%20toward%20other%20AI-related%20beneficiaries%20and%20industrials%2C%20and%20we%20expect%20this%20trend%20to%20continue%20as%20investors%20seek%20exposure%20to%20the%20broader%20AI%20supply%20chain%20and%20opportunities%20that%20are%20uncorrelated%20with%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20analysts%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20concerns%20that%20the%20rally%20has%20become%20speculative%2C%20Goldman%20said%20retail%20positioning%20does%20not%20resemble%20that%20of%20an%20overheated%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRetail%20activity%20has%20risen%2C%20but%20investor%20exposure%20remains%20well%20below%20levels%20typically%20associated%20with%20market%20excess%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bank%20also%20said%20headline%20margin-loan%20figures%20overstate%20investor%20risk%20because%20much%20of%20the%20growth%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkorean-chipmaker-stock-selloff-samsung-sk-hynix-global-market-weakness-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eleveraged%20ETF%20assets%3C%2Fa%3E%20reflects%20rising%20share%20prices%20rather%20than%20fresh%20borrowing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDomestic%20households%20have%20also%20yet%20to%20go%20all-in%20on%20Korean%20stocks%2C%20Goldman%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKorean%20households%20continue%20to%20maintain%20property-skewed%20portfolios%20rather%20than%20exhibiting%20all-in%20positioning%20toward%20domestic%20equities%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20households%20remain%20heavily%20invested%20in%20real%20estate%2C%20cash%20and%20overseas%20equities%20%E2%80%94%20particularly%20US%20stocks%20%E2%80%94%20domestic%20investors%20still%20have%20significant%20capacity%20to%20increase%20allocations%20to%20Korean%20shares%20if%20market%20conditions%20remain%20favorable%2C%20the%20analysts%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bank%20expects%20exceptionally%20strong%20earnings%20growth%20to%20continue%2C%20forecasting%20profits%20to%20rise%20320%25%20this%20year%20and%20another%2035%25%20in%202027.%20Valuations%20outside%20Samsung%20Electronics%20and%20SK%20Hynix%20remain%20reasonable%20relative%20to%20regional%20peers%2C%20Goldman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldman%20expects%20the%20Kospi%20to%20reach%2012%2C000%20over%20the%20next%2012%20months%2C%20implying%20more%20than%2020%25%20upside%20from%20current%20levels%2C%20while%20cautioning%20that%20the%20rally%20is%20likely%20to%20take%20a%20%26quot%3Bbumpy%20path.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.