r%20that%20part%20of%20the%20reason%20the%20San%20Francisco-headquartered%20vibe-coding%20startup%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbase44-ceo-maor-shlomo-built-llm-combat-ai-slop-design-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etrained%20its%20own%20LLM%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20to%20reduce%20the%20AI-slop%20look%20that%20has%20come%20to%20define%20vibe-coded%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDesign%20gurus%20have%20said%20that%20websites%20built%20with%20frontier%20models%20like%20Anthropic's%20Opus%204.8%2C%20OpenAI's%20GPT-5.5%2C%20or%20Gemini%203%20often%20share%20similar%20interfaces%20and%20design%20elements%2C%20such%20as%20rounded%20corners%2C%20beige%20color%20palettes%2C%20and%20excessive%20use%20of%20emojis.%20Base44's%20competitors%2C%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmake-app-cursor-lovable-base44-vibe-coding-tools-comparison-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELovable%20and%20Replit%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20use%20these%20underlying%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20Paul%20Bakaus%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20AI%20design%20startup%20Impeccable%2C%20said%20in%20a%20June%20interview%20with%20Andreessen%20Horowitz%20that%20the%20designs%20of%20these%20sites%20look%20like%20an%20%26quot%3Balgorithmic%20Uniqlo%20or%20Ikea%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20functional%20but%20basic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShlomo%20said%20Base%201%2C%20in%20its%20more%20advanced%20versions%20in%20the%20future%2C%20will%20%26quot%3Bcreate%20something%20that%20looked%20uniquely%20different%26quot%3B%20every%20time%2C%20but%20%26quot%3BIt's%20going%20to%20take%20some%20effort%2C%20so%20we%20are%20not%20yet%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20the%20model%20would%20produce%20faster%20results%20and%20cost%20users%20fewer%20credits%20than%20using%20frontier%20models.%20Base44%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20the%20website-building%20company%20Wix.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20see%20how%20the%20model%20fared%2C%20I%20pitted%20Base%201%20against%20Anthropic's%20Opus%204.8%20to%20vibe%20code%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvibe-coding-website-lovable-wix-ai-writing-portfolio-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20same%20website%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b5a6e0bb-315c-4cd7-a8b8-567ce41d1ad1%5C%22%3EMaking%20a%20website%20for%20a%20fictional%20mood%20lamp%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222638%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22I%20could%20select%20Base%201%20as%20my%20working%20AI%20model.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4764b5e3bd3a50082bffa6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221870%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20selected%20Base%201%20as%20my%20working%20AI%20model%20while%20building%20my%20website.%3Cp%3EScreenshot%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20settled%20on%20building%20an%20e-commerce%20website%20for%20a%20fictional%20product%20%E2%80%94%20an%20emotional%20support%20lamp%20that%20can%20read%20Google%20calendars%20and%20change%20its%20hue%20depending%20on%20the%20ongoing%20event.%20I%20asked%20it%20to%20glow%20yellow%20for%20focus%20mode%2C%20blue%20for%20downtime%2C%20pink%20for%20meetings%2C%20and%20red%20for%20impending%20deadlines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20fed%20Base44%20my%20prompt%2C%20carefully%20avoiding%20any%20instructions%20about%20website%20design%2C%20curious%20to%20see%20what%20design%20it%20would%20come%20up%20with%20on%20its%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20pressing%20Enter%2C%20I%20selected%20Base%201%20as%20my%20AI%20model.%20Free%20users%20don't%20have%20this%20option%3B%20only%20users%20with%20the%20%2440-per-month%20%26quot%3BBuilder%26quot%3B%20subscription%20or%20higher%20can%20toggle%20between%20AI%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20few%20minutes%20of%20anticipation%2C%20Base44%20presented%20me%20with%20the%20site%20for%20%26quot%3BLumos.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ba22a9f7-19a9-44fe-8347-bc04fa98da26%5C%22%3EBase%201%20vs%20Opus%204.8%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222638%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20of%20a%20vibe%20coded%20website%20created%20by%20Base44.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4614d7ec11c5f7e7fa7799%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221870%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20was%20surprised%20by%20the%20deep%20color%20palette%2C%20one%20that%20I%20had%20not%20seen%20unprompted%20on%20a%20vibe-coded%20website.%3Cp%3EScreenshot%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOff%20the%20bat%2C%20I%20was%20surprised%20by%20the%20design.%20The%20website%20had%20a%20deep%20blue%20background%2C%20which%20already%20set%20it%20apart%20from%20the%20light%20or%20beige-colored%20front%20ends%20I'd%20seen%20on%20most%20vibe-coded%20websites.%20It%20was%20complemented%20by%20a%20bright%20yellow%20accent%20color.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rest%20of%20the%20website%20was%20basic%2C%20with%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffigma-ceo-dylan-field-creative-careers-ai-graphic-design-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etelltale%20signs%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20being%20vibe-coded.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20elements%20had%20rounded%20corners%2C%20and%20there%20were%20plenty%20of%20emojis%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222230%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Base44's%20Base%201%20generated%20a%20website%20with%20plenty%20of%20emojis.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a475696e3bd3a50082bff9c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221726%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBase44's%20Base%201%20model%20generated%20a%20website%20with%20plenty%20of%20emojis.%3Cp%3EScreenshot%2FBase44%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Shlomo%20said%2C%20Base%201%20has%20a%20long%20way%20to%20go%20before%20its%20designs%20can%20be%20truly%20unique.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20comparison's%20sake%2C%20I%20fed%20Base44%20the%20same%20prompt%20again%2C%20but%20chose%20Anthropic's%20Opus%204.8%20as%20the%20working%20model%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20thing%20that%20struck%20me%20was%20that%20Opus%204.8%20took%20longer%20to%20generate%20the%20site%20than%20Base%201%2C%20which%20felt%20like%20twice%20as%20long.%20When%20it%20finally%20loaded%2C%20I%20had%20my%20first%20%26quot%3Baha!%26quot%3B%20moment%20%E2%80%94%20hello%2C%20beige%20background.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222574%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20of%20Base44-coded%20website.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a47586865e65d39ff1c95cd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221762%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20color%20palette%20of%20the%20Opus%204.8-coded%20website%20was%20more%20what%20I%20was%20used%20to%20from%20vibe-coded%20websites.%3Cp%3EScreenshot%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20the%20color%20palette%2C%20everything%20else%20was%20similar%20to%20the%20Base%201-coded%20website.%20While%20Base%201%20was%20faster%2C%20both%20used%20the%20same%20number%20of%20credits%2C%201.2%20message%20credits%20each%20out%20of%20my%20250%20monthly%20credits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20I%20tried%20tweaking%20both%20websites%20to%20add%20one%20extra%20feature.%20I%20prompted%20both%20models%20to%20add%20a%20few%20more%20color%20modes%20%E2%80%94%20green%20for%20exercise%20and%20teal%20for%20eye%20breaks.%20To%20complete%20this%20task%2C%20Opus%204.8%20burned%20through%201.4%20message%20credits%2C%20while%20Base%201%20got%20the%20job%20done%20in%201.2%20credits%20and%20made%20the%20change%20faster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20difference%20was%20small%2C%20Opus%20was%20proving%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-token-economy-spending-workplace-budgets-usage-caps-software-engineer-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eto%20use%20credits%3C%2Fa%3E%20faster%20for%20what%20was%20effectively%20the%20same%20tweak.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20things%20considered%2C%20I%20did%20not%20see%20a%20major%20difference%20in%20how%20the%20two%20models%20worked%2C%20aside%20from%20the%20Opus-generated%20design%20looking%20a%20tad%20more%20generic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShlomo%20said%20the%20Base44%20team%20will%20conduct%20%26quot%3Breinforcement%20learning%26quot%3B%20on%20Base%201%2C%20which%20involves%20prompting%20the%20model%20to%20keep%20generating%20designs%20that%20look%20new%20and%20unique.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe'll%20check%20back%20in%20when%20the%20next%20version%20is%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbase44-first-llm-base-1-ai-coded-website-comparison-anthropic-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783314048000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4763da65e65d39ff1c95d3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbase44-first-llm-base-1-ai-coded-website-comparison-anthropic-2026-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Base44%20said%20its%20new%20AI%20model%20aims%20to%20be%20faster%2C%20burn%20through%20fewer%20credits%2C%20and%20produce%20better%20designs%20than%20frontier%20models.%20We%20put%20it%20to%20the%20test.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22abharade%40insider.com%20(Aditi%20Bharade)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A96%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Stock%20Market%20LIVE%3A%20Sensex%20extends%20gains%2C%20up%20400%20pts%2C%20Nifty%20near%2024%2C400%3B%20BEL%20shares%20up%202%25%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783313644000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2026-05%2F26%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F1200X628%2F1779759203-8954.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fstock-market-live-july-6-nse-bse-sensex-today-nifty-gift-nifty-us-iran-deal-brent-crude-oil-price-q1-results-today-126070600079_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sensex%20Today%20%7C%20Stock%20Market%2