3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Father-energy-planning-to-raise-200-million-via-institutional-share-sale-126070600223_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Father-energy-planning-to-raise-200-million-via-institutional-share-sale-126070600223_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Groq's%20founder%20says%20his%20'terrible'%20leadership%20cost%20his%20company%203%20to%204%20years%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Groq%20founder%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4b26931bba93485607baad%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGroq's%20founder%20said%20that%20he%20set%20his%20company%20back%20three%20to%20four%20years%20because%20of%20leadership%20mistakes.%3Cp%3EBloomberg%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EJonathan%20Ross%20said%20his%20leadership%20mistake%20cost%20Groq%20several%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20founder%20said%20his%20leadership%20mistakes%20included%20hiring%20issues%20and%20excessive%20delegation.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20turning%20point%20for%20Ross%20was%20shifting%20from%20talent%20growth%20to%20talent%20selection.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EJonathan%20Ross%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-exec-ai-likes-to-use-ai-it-impacts-resumes-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGroq's%20former%20CEO%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20his%20steep%20learning%20curve%20as%20a%20founder%20came%20at%20a%20hefty%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20a%20terrible%20leader.%20I%20was%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20worst%20leaders%20when%20I%20started%2C%26quot%3B%20Ross%20said%20on%20an%20episode%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BFounders%26quot%3B%20podcast%20released%20on%20Sunday.%20He%20recounted%20his%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Emanagement%20mistakes%20early%20in%20the%20chipmaker's%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20thing%20that%20you%20have%20to%20do%20as%20a%20founder%20is%20you%20have%20to%20go%20from%20the%20technical%20thing%20that%20you%20know%20how%20to%20do%20and%20that%20you%20can%20add%20value%20with%2C%20to%20learning%20how%20to%20manage%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Ross%20said.%20%26quot%3BFor%20me%2C%20that%20probably%20cost%20Groq%20three%20to%20four%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoss%2C%20a%20former%20Google%20engineer%2C%20cofounded%20Groq%20in%202016%20to%20build%20chips%20it%20calls%20language%20processing%20units.%20The%20custom%20AI%20inference%20chips%20are%20an%20alternative%20to%20Nvidia's%20graphics%20processing%20units.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20December%2C%20Nvidia%20struck%20a%20roughly%20%2420%20billion%20licensing%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-groq-deals-silicon-valley-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etalent%20deal%20with%20Groq%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20bringing%20Ross%2C%20Groq%20president%20Sunny%20Madra%2C%20and%20other%20key%20engineers%20to%20Nvidia%20while%20allowing%20Groq%20to%20remain%20an%20independent%20company.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Nvidia%2C%20Ross%20serves%20as%20chief%20software%20architect%2C%20while%20Groq%20is%20helmed%20by%20Adam%20Winter%2C%20a%20former%20vice%20president%20at%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20founder%2C%20Ross%20said%20he%20erred%20in%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Enot%20hiring%20people%20who%20could%20operate%20autonomously%2C%20and%20then%20delegating%20them%20too%20much%20responsibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20ended%20up%20happening%20was%20things%20would%20just%20grind%20to%20a%20halt%20because%20they%20wouldn't%20know%20what%20to%20do%2C%20and%20I%20wasn't%20telling%20them%20what%20to%20do%2C%20and%20they%20were%20used%20to%20being%20told%20what%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20founder%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoss%20said%20the%20turning%20point%20was%20when%20he%20became%20more%20selective%20about%20hiring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20went%20from%20looking%20for%20positives%2C%20which%20is%20what%20you%20do%20when%20you're%20trying%20to%20grow%20talent%2C%20to%20looking%20for%20negatives%2C%20which%20is%20what%20you%20do%20when%20you're%20trying%20to%20select%20talent%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20tech%20founders%20have%20detailed%20similar%20early-days%20management%20mistakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20December%20podcast%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffigma-ceo-says-he-was-bad-manager-turned-around-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFigma%20CEO%20Dylan%20Field%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20he%20confused%20leadership%20with%20management.%20He%20said%20he%20had%20to%20learn%20basics%20like%20holding%20one-on-one%20meetings%2C%20building%20relationships%2C%20and%20creating%20accountability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BManagement%20and%20leadership%20are%20different%2C%26quot%3B%20Field%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20be%20a%20good%20leader%20and%20a%20bad%20manager%20or%20vice%20versa.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20May%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fduolingo-ceo-leadership-style-how-career-changed-company-grew-micromanager-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20Duolingo%20CEO%20Luis%20von%20Ahn%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20all%20founders%20should%20be%20micromanagers%20until%20they%20had%2030%20employees%20%E2%80%94%20but%20that%20he%20took%20it%20too%20far%2C%20micromanaging%20until%20he%20had%2050.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20this%20point%2C%20I%20also%20have%20learned%20that%20most%20of%20my%20job%20is%20culture%20carrier%2C%20mascot%2C%20and%20just%20making%20some%20of%20the%20kind%20of%20tough%20philosophical%20decisions%2C%26quot%3B%20von%20Ahn%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgroq-founder-jonathan-ross-leadership-mistakes-nvidia-delegation-hiring-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusine